1. START THE LOCAL DEV SERVER
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

This is a static site. There is NO "npm start" script. Use one of these:

  RECOMMENDED (no install needed):
    npx serve . -p 3000

  ALTERNATIVE — Python:
    python3 -m http.server 3000

  ALTERNATIVE — Netlify CLI (runs functions too):
    npm install -g netlify-cli
    netlify dev

Site is served at:   http://localhost:3000
Admin panel:         http://localhost:3000/admin.html
Admin menu:          http://localhost:3000/admin-menu.html
Executive admin:     http://localhost:3000/admin-executive.html
PAI Hub:             http://localhost:3000/Platforms-Apps-Infrastructure/


