2. NPM SCRIPTS (package.json)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

All scripts run from the repo root (/workspaces/skyesol):

  npm run build
    → Regenerates the admin site menu (site-map JSON used by admin tools).
    → Script: scripts/generate-site-menu.mjs
    → Run after adding new pages or renaming directories.
    → Skips: node_modules, .git, xxDEVONLY, AI DIRECTIVES, template files.

  npm run gen-sitemap
    → Regenerates sitemap.xml for SEO.
    → Script: scripts/generate-sitemap.js
    → Site URL: https://skyesol.netlify.app
    → Run whenever pages are added, removed, or renamed.
    → Priority/changefreq per page are hardcoded in that script — update them
      there if you add new core pages.

  npm run link-check
    → Scans all HTML files for broken internal links and missing rel attributes.
    → Script: scripts/link-guardian.js
    → Read-only (reports only, does not modify files).

  npm run link-check:fix
    → Same as link-check but also auto-patches fixable issues (like missing
      rel="noopener noreferrer" on external links).
    → Script: scripts/link-guardian.js --fix
    → MODIFIES FILES — run before committing.

  npm run audit:internal-links
    → Deep audit of internal href targets across all HTML.
    → Script: scripts/audit-internal-links.mjs
    → Reports 404-style broken internal links.

  npm run meta:check
    → Checks all HTML files for missing or incomplete <meta> tags (title,
      description, og:image, etc.).
    → Script: scripts/meta-templater.js --check
    → Read-only.

  npm run meta:apply
    → Applies the default and per-page meta tags defined in meta-templater.js
      to all HTML files.
    → Script: scripts/meta-templater.js
    → MODIFIES FILES. Run carefully — review diffs after.
    → Default og:image: https://cdn1.sharemyimage.com/2026/02/23/ChatGPTImageFeb23202610_24_00AM.png


