3. STANDALONE MAINTENANCE SCRIPTS
   (run directly with node)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

  node scripts/sync-blogs-manifest.js
    → Rebuilds Blogs/blog-manifest.json by scanning the Blogs/ directory.
    → Run after adding, removing, or renaming blog post HTML files.
    → The blog feed (blog.html) reads from this manifest.

  node scripts/sync-case-studies-index.js
    → Rebuilds the Case Studies index from the Case Studies/ directory.
    → Run after adding or removing case study files.


