4. GIT WORKFLOW
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

  Repo:     skyesoverlondon-alt/skyesol
  Branch:   main (default + production)
  Host:     Netlify — auto-deploys on push to main

  Standard commit & push:
    git add -A
    git commit -m "your message"
    git push origin main

  Stage specific file:
    git add index.html

  Files with spaces in path (quote them):
    git add "Skye Identity Standard: Global Command Center/index.html"

  Check what's staged / dirty:
    git status

  View recent commits:
    git log --oneline -10

  Undo last commit (keep changes):
    git reset --soft HEAD~1

  Discard unstaged changes to a file:
    git checkout -- filename.html


