6. COMMON MAINTENANCE TASKS
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

  AFTER ADDING A NEW PAGE:
    1. Add entry to sitemap.xml (or run npm run gen-sitemap)
    2. Add link to partials/header.html nav dropdown
    3. Add card to platforms.html and/or PAI hub index.html if it's an app
    4. Add entry to admin menu (admin-menu.html) if it's an admin tool
    5. npm run build  (regenerates site menu for admin tools)
    6. git add -A && git commit -m "..." && git push origin main

  AFTER ADDING BLOG POSTS:
    1. Drop HTML file into Blogs/ subdirectory
    2. node scripts/sync-blogs-manifest.js
    3. git add -A && git commit && git push

  AFTER ADDING CASE STUDIES:
    1. Drop HTML file into Case Studies/
    2. node scripts/sync-case-studies-index.js
    3. git add -A && git commit && git push

  CHECK FOR BROKEN LINKS:
    npm run link-check

  FIX MISSING META TAGS:
    npm run meta:check   (see what's missing)
    npm run meta:apply   (apply fixes)

  FULL AUDIT BEFORE DEPLOY:
    npm run link-check
    npm run audit:internal-links
    npm run meta:check


